  pages     = {200--211},
  note      = {Increased collective efficacy, but also increased intergroup prejudice...},
  abstract  = {Does social influence exerted through role modeling of collective action impact social change in contexts that are
not conducive to collective action, such as long-lasting violent conflicts?We examined this question in two field
